{"tid":268052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那民運領袖無承諾保證香港獨立, 為何要幫佢地平反及建設民主暴政？","createTime":"2017-06-02T17:18:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T11:17:04.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ff78fa256441678acbadfc98498369aea9b35a3e","tid":268052,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T17:18:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.read01.com/uploads/0CdMT700.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.read01.com%2Fuploads%2F0CdMT700.jpg&h=66e90402&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n意大利統一戰爭時, 意大利領袖報答聖馬利諾收留領袖<br />\n統一戰爭勝利後簽署條約, 永久保障聖馬利諾主權獨立<br />\n(見《香港獨立論》)<br />\n<br />\n其實支那人 (包括流亡海外既所謂民運領袖) 從來都無承諾過<br />\n一旦民主支那出現後, 會保障香港獨特自治領 / 獨立主權國地位<br />\n<br />\n正如1982年時, 支那國從來無保障香港有普選有民主時間表<br />\n就豬一樣地講「民主回歸」<br />\n<br />\n搞六四民主支那, 根本就豬過聖馬利諾<br />\n更加係重蹈1982年既錯誤覆轍"},{"pid":"daa3d7aee7c8a2172684114bd1a8c4dfd8859b6b","tid":268052,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T17:21:46.000Z","msg":"唔好侮辱意大利人"},{"pid":"2149ecce7170c289fe51bb8b96482c7b960d7940","tid":268052,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T17:24:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好侮辱意大利人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n意大利人好有承諾"},{"pid":"d61d65980f23b6e845f8a2fdfb495f509b6791ab","tid":268052,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:52:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e38d55d411e6d9ff24849e88aa04260f34eb46c6","tid":268052,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:54:17.000Z","msg":"所謂民運領袖都係當香港人係下等人，我記得有中國維權人仕恥笑香港媽媽買唔到奶粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36df34553b64c1f12be752ee0e5f0da64e565786","tid":268052,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:59:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所謂民運領袖都係當香港人係下等人，我記得有中國維權人仕恥笑香港媽媽買唔到奶粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://dadazim.com/journal/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/beast.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdadazim.com%2Fjournal%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F01%2Fbeast.jpg&h=da23c811&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢條仆街依家去左美帝happy了！<br />\n<br />\n同柴玲一鳩樣"},{"pid":"f605f744591f023f40395939757e068c004a9d45","tid":268052,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:59:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>所謂民運領袖都係當香港人係下等人，我記得有中國維權人仕恥笑香港媽媽買唔到奶粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://dadazim.com/journal/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/beast.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdadazim.com%2Fjournal%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F01%2Fbeast.jpg&h=da23c811&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢條仆街依家去左美帝happy了！<br />\n<br />\n同柴玲一鳩樣</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-mZQ4g2cINFY/UQK7l3bvGTI/AAAAAAAADcc/dGa3ai61NPY/s640/wanwanchiu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-mZQ4g2cINFY%2FUQK7l3bvGTI%2FAAAAAAAADcc%2FdGa3ai61NPY%2Fs640%2Fwanwanchiu.jpg&h=243fb9aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4e27274a2dd7baba5ee4e9afd18efc3a3501f82","tid":268052,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T06:16:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8f8e46c10592479b37aa6cd604ace2c7054e608","tid":268052,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T09:02:32.000Z","msg":"無人答到?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec3753682c1899944cfe20593702bf0d2438a964","tid":268052,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T09:07:30.000Z","msg":"平反左64對香港/香港人有乜好處？"},{"pid":"598f6e3b52d2da512fbe90ae1839607260fd17d8","tid":268052,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T09:09:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平反左64對香港/香港人有乜好處？</blockquote><br />\n諗落好似一樣都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只係某啲實質支持大一統既海外流亡人士可以返中國<br />\n不了，無我地著數既"},{"pid":"87fedf30b50e18489ccbce1f888d4ba6155e33aa","tid":268052,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T09:16:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>平反左64對香港/香港人有乜好處？</blockquote><br />\n諗落好似一樣都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只係某啲實質支持大一統既海外流亡人士可以返中國<br />\n不了，無我地著數既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正是！<br />\n<br />\n係都要支那民運人士公開承諾, 簽署條約<br />\n民主支那出現, 保障香港獨立<br />\n有咁既先決條件, 先去搞乜野支援建設民主支那啦！"},{"pid":"c4886ecd79ba36cbe116cea80e7c4a6d2eb5625e","tid":268052,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T09:27:38.000Z","msg":"去64晚會牙斬斬嗰班, <br />\n<br />\n無人答到？"},{"pid":"b4a03b415c72fb9479fc38636ba2cbeb4d0133a7","tid":268052,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T09:30:02.000Z","msg":"王丹有無講過, 支那民主化後,<br />\n<br />\n香港會保障獨立主權先？<br />\n<br />\n無喎, 28年黎半句承諾都無喎<br />\n<br />\n點先？仲去鳩坐做乜春？"},{"pid":"96933bffb86881546b8a8fae0cdd97c49a72e34f","tid":268052,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T09:34:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>王丹有無講過, 支那民主化後,<br />\n<br />\n香港會保障獨立主權先？<br />\n<br />\n無喎, 28年黎半句承諾都無喎<br />\n<br />\n點先？仲去鳩坐做乜春？</blockquote><br />\n佢地咩身份先？就算將來真係有民主中國，佢地一定位高權重？<br />\n佢地點作出承諾"},{"pid":"35b92a570dbb13c1bf8993107a911bd88aae7325","tid":268052,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T09:35:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>王丹有無講過, 支那民主化後,<br />\n<br />\n香港會保障獨立主權先？<br />\n<br />\n無喎, 28年黎半句承諾都無喎<br />\n<br />\n點先？仲去鳩坐做乜春？</blockquote><br />\n佢地咩身份先？就算將來真係有民主中國，佢地一定位高權重？<br />\n佢地點作出承諾</blockquote><br />\n不過佢地連空頭承諾都唔敢作出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db6bdab87a957487211b53ad0535bef04e8ba1dd","tid":268052,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T09:39:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>王丹有無講過, 支那民主化後,<br />\n<br />\n香港會保障獨立主權先？<br />\n<br />\n無喎, 28年黎半句承諾都無喎<br />\n<br />\n點先？仲去鳩坐做乜春？</blockquote><br />\n佢地咩身份先？就算將來真係有民主中國，佢地一定位高權重？<br />\n佢地點作出承諾</blockquote><br />\n不過佢地連空頭承諾都唔敢作出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n起碼有一大班所謂「民運領袖」及「維權律師」認頭, 簽署條約<br />\n先講啦, 係咪？<br />\n<br />\n都未有條約承諾, 我仲乜鬼要去平反鄰國既事？"},{"pid":"67235faa8043deaf0b763efb2933b3251ce6f610","tid":268052,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T10:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"560bb53164bcefde13b0bf7516ea459fee78353e","tid":268052,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T10:37:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9571d1078147e548c5d69dbd123d8eb357dbc3ec","tid":268052,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T10:58:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbc86a70faab49e2504b141466bb70c4944da1e4","tid":268052,"uid":349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T11:03:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去64晚會牙斬斬嗰班, <br />\n<br />\n無人答到？</blockquote><br />\n因為個班大中華情結既人，佢地目標唔係要香港獨立或者有自治權。佢地理想係香港成為民主中國下既一部分。香港有冇自治權佢地don't give a fuck（我估）"},{"pid":"78d629a3e8220f09563384293cd30dd00d3afb6d","tid":268052,"uid":54627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T11:15:48.000Z","msg":"跟低賤的支那人說「承諾」是愚蠢的"},{"pid":"b4641263f59a2c142d50e630d0cc60d93cf91ccd","tid":268052,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T11:16:51.000Z","msg":"[<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> quote]跟低賤的支那人說「承諾」是愚蠢的[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n但我地連低賤既承諾也沒有"},{"pid":"fc7b3fcd0b7e6e10d4312437282f0f806068b0c5","tid":268052,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T11:17:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跟低賤的支那人說「承諾」是愚蠢的</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我地連低賤既承諾也沒有<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}